| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0750 — Recovery Inhibition (funksec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9eb0014f-42b4-53c1-8ff7-205e2d934c94"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
